{"tid":9574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"道歉法報告出爐　適用所有民事程序　本立法年度引入","createTime":"2016-11-28T15:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T16:16:30.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10a9d06186e7927c158f8c68f47409567ede92c3","tid":9574,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:45:16.000Z","msg":"道歉法報告出爐　適用所有民事程序　本立法年度引入<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161128/s00001/1480320405896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161128%2Fs00001%2F1480320405896&d=%2BH5Ct%2BqKl88PKFNa36s1l8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=427d2046\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161128%2Fs00001%2F1480320405896&h=01afb4fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161128/s00001/1480320405896</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161128/s00001/1480335126067SL4_51328F75EE82BD611070D944A4D404EA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161128%2Fs00001%2F1480335126067SL4_51328F75EE82BD611070D944A4D404EA.jpg&h=fc235e59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n調解督導委員會發表《在香港制定道歉法例：最終報告及建議》，2016／17立法年度引入道歉法。<br />\n<br />\n道歉法第二輪公眾諮詢早前結束，委員會收到60份書面回應，包括政府、法定組織或規管機構、政黨、學者等。<br />\n<br />\n委員會建議，道歉法例應適用於所有民事法律程序，包括紀律處分程序和規管法律程序，但根據《調查委員會條例》（第86章）、《死因裁判官條例》（第504 章）及《淫褻及不雅物品管制條例》（第390章）執行的程序則屬例外。<br />\n<br />\n委員會亦建議道歉法例應保護道歉中傳達的事實資料，法院或審裁處在適用程序中應具有酌情權，顧及所有相關情況後如認為屬公正和公平，便可接納這類事實陳述作為不利道歉者的證據。<br />\n<br />\n委員會指出，律政司同意相關建議，將會推展相關工作，2016／17立法年度引入道歉法。報告已上載至律政司網頁(<a href=\"http://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/public/apology.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.doj.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fpublic%2Fapology.html&d=%2BH5Ct%2BqKl88PKFNa36s1l8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=41587d44\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/public/apology.html</a>)。<br />\n<br />\n制訂道歉法旨在藉釐清道歉的法律後果，提倡和鼓勵道歉，促使爭議各方達成和解。"},{"pid":"4c9012684ccddda998937cd4831a437a0281d08a","tid":9574,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:03:17.000Z","msg":"乜撚野 咁戇鳩"},{"pid":"4273cd56e5f433b7f2d37b466939e4d466cbe99b","tid":9574,"uid":25328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:16:30.000Z","msg":"乜嘢道歉法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}